{"title":"vscode 有趣的功能","uid":"57ebfbfb1ef0759746dce75d6b8c9c2e","slug":"vscode-new","date":"2025-04-02T02:14:09.384Z","updated":"2026-02-11T06:05:14.087Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/vscode-new.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMbZ-yjGIZcnEH_cicwtqyOho5vnxYAAsrDMRu16WhXOmkHZAKLCt4BAAMCAAN5AAM2BA.png","content":"<p>本文主要记录一些 vscode 的有趣功能，可能会不定期更新。每次 vscode 更新都会有一个更新文档，文档中会详细介绍新功能和修复的 bug，感兴趣的可以去看看，在顶部 Help =&gt; Shou Release Notes 下。或者打开<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/updates/\">vscode 官方更新文档</a>查看历史更新日志。</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-99\">1.99</h2>\n<h3 id=\"copilot-现在支持自定义Key了-Anthropic-Azure-Gmini-OpenAI-Ollama-OpenRouter\">copilot 现在支持自定义Key了 (Anthropic, Azure, Gmini, OpenAI, Ollama, OpenRouter)</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>在chat中选择模型<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMeZ_eUBN2hFDO-B-4COoOZzh8AATpYAAKeyTEbwJm4VymbUl7K9WbIAQADAgADeAADNgQ.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>选择 <code>Manage Models...</code> 进入模型管理界面选择 <code>OpenRouter</code> 后输入从openrouter网站创建的key<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMfZ_eUni4e1LjhNXl05xPFhm8ODwIAAqXJMRvAmbhXKuknNLhoSSEBAAMCAAN5AAM2BA.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>选择想要添加的模型<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMgZ_eVKAwbG0IJLvbT-yGkIXfy6dEAAqzJMRvAmbhXF5tychcX-mMBAAMCAAN5AAM2BA.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"copilot-新增支持-MCP-服务\">copilot 新增支持 <code>MCP</code> 服务</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>首先在设置中打开<code>⚙️chat.agent.enabled</code></li>\n<li>在chat中选择 <code>Agent</code> 模式<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMhZ_eWYQABeLX3WvZP6HQFhk4_4s2PAALByTEbwJm4V4MK0mODdCWAAQADAgADeAADNgQ.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li>点击工具按钮并选择 <code>Add MCP Server...</code><br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMiZ_eW1QoQ1DedUmpmSgQi0_VPOCEAAsjJMRvAmbhXGV_a1FUmz7sBAAMCAAN5AAM2BA.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li>选择想要的安装方式，这里以<code>NPM Package</code>安装为例<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMjZ_eXCX964-vjphqAfc31I01Si-AAAszJMRvAmbhXDh7Iv4SDw70BAAMCAAN5AAM2BA.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li>输入要安装的MCP工具名称，例如 <code>@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem</code> 并回车<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMkZ_eXfDpREmPw8MIIrriis5QyI0oAAs3JMRvAmbhXBKLvm85oeuEBAAMCAAN5AAM2BA.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li>选择允许<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMlZ_eX3SUhkxtLD0C04wZDCJ5zgZ0AAtzJMRvAmbhXA5u8l_P0450BAAMCAAN5AAM2BA.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li>按照提示输入运行工具访问的本地路径并回车(需要输入两个路径，后面可以在配置文件中修改)<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMmZ_eYNVWBO624E59Nd3JIMiGzCo8AAunJMRvAmbhXXTwm0cvVBGgBAAMCAAN5AAM2BA.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li>调整服务的唯一ID并回车<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMnZ_eYrMkmo-8y_b4FKtBL4tR1d24AAvHJMRvAmbhXXiHGNsYTk0sBAAMCAAN5AAM2BA.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li>然后会跳转到配置文件中, 这时可以调整服务的配置<br>\n<img src=\"https://img.kidwen.top/file/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAMoZ_eZKXs4ELvE5W6wovs-hRoCP8QAAvjJMRvAmbhX3fl2Gqzs9MABAAMCAAN3AAM2BA.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/servers\">mcp server modelcontextprotocol 列表</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://smithery.ai/\">mcp server smithery 列表</a></li>\n</ol></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"v1-98\">v1.98</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code>⚙️@id:workbench.settings.useWeightedKeySearch</code></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5